    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of injection of Surgiflo as a sealent in treatment of pilonidal sinus, evaluation
      includes recurrence, infection, complications and patient satisfaction over 2 years of follow
      up
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
